additional_house_rules: Minimum booking is for two days.  We will accept 1 day bookings for $150.00 minimum for bookings from Monday thru Friday, but not on the weekend.  Weekend minimum for one day booking is $200.  Guests staying longer than one day, pay the prevailing rate.
description:
Our place is close to public transport, 12 miles to JFK, 1/2 block to scenic Sheepshead Bay, 1 block to the ocean & sandy beaches, less than 1/2 hour to Manhattan by car & 45 minutes by subway & 10-20 minute walk to many fine restaurants.

Modern 2BR apartment with queen bed in master & trundle in 2nd BR.  New modern granite kitchen with all amenities.  Comfortable LR with dining area.  High speed WiFi, cable, all premium movie channels with 50" TV.  Half-block walk to Sheepshead Bay and one block to sandy beaches & ocean.  10-20 minute walk to fine dining.  Public transportation 1/2 block away.

Apartment has private, keyed entrance.

Transportation is 1/2 block away.  If you like to walk, 20 minutes will get you to shopping & fine dining.  Beach is 1 block away.

hosts.about: Native New Yorker.  Friendly and outgoing.  Enjoy hosting, travelling, sailing, skiing and movies.  Great in the kitchen.
